EC50_MICROM: Effective concentration of half maximal event count as estimated by curve fit
EC50_95CI_LOW: Lower 95% confidence interval boundary for the EC50 curve fit estimate
EC50_95CI_HIGH: Upper 95% confidence interval boundary for the EC50 curve fit estimate
HILLSLOPE: Hill slope estimate for the fitted dose response curve
FIT_PERCENT_SPAN: Percent response based on bottom and top span from EC50 curve fit estimate
RSQR: Correlation coefficient for the fitted dose response curve
N_POINTS: Number of data points for each dose response curve
